rating_comment: Excellent behaviour. The host was really very cooperative and very friendly. He guided us from the time we started our journey. The climate of the place is very hot so he arranged extra fans which is really appreciated. Any one can go and stay. I really felt a homely atmosphere. I wish him all the best for his future.
We had a wonderful time staying. His house was even more beautiful in person that in the photos. We love his Breakfast, lunch & dinner. Thanks for everything Kumud Ranjan.
Very good host and pleasant stay. Close to the station (walking distance)and other visitable places (via Toto)
